metadata.name: Dark day
metadata.description: The portrait of a red-haired girl, made with acrylic paints, had an unearthly quality. Her expression was mysterious and mesmerizing, but something seemed to be missing. There was a hint of sadness and longing in her eyes, as if she was looking for something and still hadn't found it. When the viewer looked into her eyes, they were lost in a world of mysterious emotions and sensations. This portrait exquisitely conveyed the beauty and depth of the girl, which made it a work of art that will never be forgotten.
